  <span id="freeText9154847873967587126" style="display:none">4.5 Stars<br />A brilliant storyline based on indian mythology. I wasn't keen on starting this series because I don't like it when facts that I have read from mythologies change. But the author has done an amazing work in building all the characters! <br />People who aren't familiar with mythologies won't be confused when they read this.</span>
